901
00:48:51,829 --> 00:48:54,958
We must not fail him either.

902
00:48:55,032 --> 00:48:57,058
[Hands clapping]

903
00:49:05,042 --> 00:49:08,410
Just as we must not fail
his victim.

904
00:49:09,313 --> 00:49:12,715
The punishment must fit
the crime.

905
00:49:12,783 --> 00:49:16,185
Only by implementing a tougher,
harsher regime,

906
00:49:16,253 --> 00:49:18,779
can we hope to decriminalize
the criminal.

907
00:49:19,657 --> 00:49:22,422
Rehabilitation is still
our priority.

908
00:49:22,493 --> 00:49:25,463
It must become our prisoners'.

909
00:49:25,529 --> 00:49:28,988
[Triumphant music plays]

910
00:49:59,363 --> 00:50:01,093
Bring all your personal
belongings with you,

911
00:50:01,165 --> 00:50:03,600
