back on the bus!

912
00:50:03,667 --> 00:50:06,569
Come along!
Get in line and move along!

913
00:50:06,637 --> 00:50:09,266
Two orderly lines! Come on!
Move it! Move it!

914
00:50:09,340 --> 00:50:12,276
[Triumphant music continues]

915
00:50:12,343 --> 00:50:15,040
[Indistinct conversations]

916
00:50:16,113 --> 00:50:19,083
Will you get a bloody move on?!

917
00:50:19,149 --> 00:50:22,244
Pick your feet up,
you disgusting little man!

918
00:50:22,319 --> 00:50:24,117
When I say move, I mean move!

919
00:50:24,188 --> 00:50:26,282
What do you think you are,
the bloody circus?!

920
